data.description:
*Sellers are offering $2500 in closing costs assistance.* Nestled in the heart of Weems, Virginia near Compass Entertainment Complex in Irvington, this home is a true gem. With a shed boasting a loft and an attached carport, this property is the perfect blend of modern convenience and classic charm, complete with a bonus room that can be used as an additional bedroom, office, or playroom. The primary bedroom includes an ensuite bathroom. 
The interior has been freshly painted, giving the home a clean and inviting atmosphere that's ready for your personal touch. The property features a cozy deck, perfect for entertaining, and a shed with a loft that provides plenty of storage space for your hobbies or additional living space. The beautiful natural surroundings of Weems, Virginia, offer a tranquil setting to call home.
This is your opportunity to own a charming and updated home in a prime location near the Compass Entertainment Complex in Weems, Virginia as well as other shops and entertainment. Don't miss out on the chance to make this delightful property your own. Schedule a viewing today and start envisioning the possibilities of your new life in this wonderful home!
